USER STORIES:

  PIGEON COURIER SYSTEM:
                          In USA there is courier system which is available in various countries:they
                          collect pet animals,parcels,letter,households and containers and so on for transporting purpose.
           
  MAIN TRANSPORT:  
                     Their main transport  is based on air,water and road,customer bill based on weightage
                     and space of occupancy of the goods.
                    
                                           
   BILLING SYSTEM:
                        The billing system plays key role it is based on weighttage,distance of travel,country and
                        their policies,and based on country currency.
                          
